    <item>
      <title>特朗普下令终止“电动汽车强制令”和补贴</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/trump-orders-end-to-electric-vehicle-mandate-subsidies</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统唐纳德·特朗普已下令其政府“取消电动汽车强制令”——他试图取消有关汽车污染和燃油经济性标准的规定，他认为这些规定不公平地限制了消费者的选择。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/trump-orders-end-to-electric-vehicle-mandate-subsidies</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 21 Jan 2025 02:38:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普再次呼吁欧盟购买更多美国能源以避免关税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/trump-again-calls-for-eu-to-buy-more-us-energy-to-avoid-tariffs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统唐纳德·特朗普再次呼吁欧盟购买更多美国石油和天然气，以避免关税。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/trump-again-calls-for-eu-to-buy-more-us-energy-to-avoid-tariffs</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 21 Jan 2025 02:14:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国被捕总统将出席弹劾审判</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/south-korea-s-arrested-president-to-appear-at-impeachment-trial</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国总统尹锡烈预计将于周二首次出席弹劾审判。由于上周末他在另一家法院出庭时发生了类似国会山的骚乱，因此法院加强了安保。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/south-korea-s-arrested-president-to-appear-at-impeachment-trial</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 21 Jan 2025 01:52:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普因亨特·拜登笔记本电脑信件取消安全许可</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/trump-pulls-security-clearances-over-hunter-biden-laptop-letter</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普总统撤销了 50 名前美国情报官员的安全许可，这些官员曾对保守派攻击前总统乔·拜登儿子表示怀疑，特朗普兑现了竞选承诺，对他所认为的针对他的“深层政府”阴谋进行报复。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/trump-pulls-security-clearances-over-hunter-biden-laptop-letter</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 21 Jan 2025 01:47:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普暂停 TikTok 禁令，给应用程序更多时间寻找买家</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/trump-halts-tiktok-ban-giving-app-extra-time-to-find-a-buyer</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统唐纳德·特朗普暂时停止了对 TikTok 在美国的禁令，给予该公司及其中国母公司字节跳动有限公司更多时间就这款热门应用程序达成协议，以解决长期存在的美国国家安全担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/trump-halts-tiktok-ban-giving-app-extra-time-to-find-a-buyer</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 21 Jan 2025 01:16:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普赦免 1500 多名美国国会骚乱被告</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/trump-says-he-s-pardoning-nearly-all-capitol-riot-defendants</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普赦免了几乎所有因参与 2021 年 1 月 6 日袭击美国国会大厦而被定罪的人，并下令撤销所有未决案件的指控，兑现了他返回白宫数小时后备受争议的竞选承诺。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/trump-says-he-s-pardoning-nearly-all-capitol-riot-defendants</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 21 Jan 2025 01:03:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普计划在 2 月 1 日前对墨西哥、加拿大征收 25% 关税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/trump-plans-to-enact-25-tariffs-on-mexico-canada-by-feb-1</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统唐纳德·特朗普表示，他计划在 2 月 1 日之前实施之前威胁的对墨西哥和加拿大征收高达 25% 的关税，重申了他的观点，即美国的两个近邻允许无证移民和毒品流入该国。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/trump-plans-to-enact-25-tariffs-on-mexico-canada-by-feb-1</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 21 Jan 2025 00:57:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马斯克获得白宫电子邮件地址和办公空间，将领导 DOGE</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-20/billionaire-elon-musk-secures-white-house-email-address</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亿万富翁埃隆·马斯克已经获得了白宫电子邮件地址和办公空间，为他启动所谓的“政府效率部”成本削减计划铺平了道路。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-20/billionaire-elon-musk-secures-white-house-email-address</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 20 Jan 2025 23:43:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普行政措施概述，从关税到移民</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-20/trump-executive-orders-tariffs-immigration-energy-among-top-priorities</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普总统立即宣布了实施其许多竞选承诺的措施，包括移民、能源、军事和联邦劳动力等方面的政策，其中许多政策被视为推翻其前任乔·拜登的政策。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-20/trump-executive-orders-tariffs-immigration-energy-among-top-priorities</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 20 Jan 2025 21:12:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巴拿马对中国港口运营商展开审计，特朗普威胁收回运河</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-20/panama-opens-audit-of-chinese-port-operator-amid-trump-s-threats</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在唐纳德·特朗普总统再次威胁接管巴拿马运河之际，巴拿马当局开始对控制巴拿马运河附近两个港口的中国相关公司进行审计。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-20/panama-opens-audit-of-chinese-port-operator-amid-trump-s-threats</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 20 Jan 2025 19:10:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
